@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 02. Supervisor Agent Package Policy (Python runtime: src/app)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "src/app" {
  package "api" {
    class supervisor_a2a_endpoint
    class supervisor_a2a_request_validator
  }

  package "application" {
    package "execution" {
      class supervisor_agent_service
      class task_queue_service
      class worker_execution_service
      class supervisor_graph_execution_service
      class supervisor_progress_publisher
      class supervisor_exception_translator
    }
    package "persistence" {
      class supervisor_execution_persistence_service
      class supervisor_persistence_strategy_factory
      class execution_consistency_coordinator
      class task_event_stream_service
    }
    package "read" {
      class supervisor_read_facade
      class supervisor_read_query_factory
      class task_read_model_query
      class snapshot_verification_query
    }
    class hitl_gate_service
  }

  package "services" {
    class fact_governance_service
    class prompt_injection_guard
    class handoff_policy_service
  }

  package "adapters" {
    package "llm" {
      class llm_planning_service
      class llm_compose_service
    }
    package "orchestration" {
      class langgraph_factory
      class handoff_policy
    }
    package "integration" {
      class default_a2a_invocation
    }
    package "store" {
      class redis_stores
    }
  }

  package "domain" {
    class models
    class enums
    class exceptions
  }

  package "common" {
    class canonical_json
  }
}

note bottom
Rules
- api endpoint는 JSON-RPC/SSE 입구와 params 검증만 담당한다
- supervisor_agent_service는 use case orchestration만 담당한다
- task_queue_service는 Redis 기반 Producer-Consumer 큐잉을 담당한다
- worker_execution_service는 백그라운드 워커의 실행 제어를 담당한다
- hitl_gate_service는 planner의 `review_required` 분기와 review lifecycle을 담당한다
- prompt_injection_guard는 입력 보안 검증을 담당한다
- fact_governance_service는 Swarm State의 무결성 관리를 담당한다
- execution_consistency_coordinator는 Redis CAS 기반 상태 전이를 캡슐화한다
- snapshot_verification_query는 승인 시점의 무결성 및 드리프트 검증을 담당한다
end note
@enduml
